    <description>This record triggered flow runs when the &quot;_IsAutoCreated&quot; checkbox is set to TRUE on an Interaction Log. After the Save, we check which Weekly Summary note the Interaction Logs Summary Note is taken from on the Related Deal Record and then reclassify the Type of Interaction accordingly.</description>
